GSD.description:
media: coda: Add check for kmalloc

This is an automated ID intended to aid in discovery of potential security vulnerabilities. The actual impact and attack plausibility have not yet been proven.
This ID is fixed in Linux Kernel version v5.10.163 by commit d9b37ea8869e4e6da90c07a310d819a78cbd23d2, it was introduced in version v3.19 by commit cb1d3a336371e35c3920cc50a701c5403c255644. For more details please see the references link.
